Real glass - real protection. A highly touch-sensitive, scratch resistant glass for your Samsung Galaxy M21s, with a perfect fit all the way out to the edges of the screen for maximum protection. It's oleophobic, meaning it repels dust, water and other grime, as well as the natural oils your skin produces. Easy to attach, and even easier to use! Designed to be used with most standard covers and cases.

Package included:

1 x Oleophobic touch sensitive tempered glass
1 x Wipes Set

It can be folded, allowing the phone to stand on its own. Furthermore, the small magnetic lock does not wrap around on the back and is easily flipped open with your thumb (or finger of choice), giving this a less bulky look, while not compromising a good seal to keep the case closed when not used. It's molded to perfectly fit your Nokia C1. Additionally, it has a receiver cutout, allowing you to talk even if the case is closed.
